        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Calculated value. The European production volume is extrapolated from the Global production volume  using the average GDP (constant 2017 international USD from 2015-2019). The annual Global production volume in the year 2021 is 30'660'000'000 kg. This value is multiplied with the European share of global GDP, 19.6%.

References:
Statista, 2022, Market volume of ethylene oxide worldwide from 2015 to 2021, with a forecast for 2022 to 2029, available here: https://www.statista.com/statistics/1245260/ethylene-oxide-market-volume-worldwide/, accessed 16-12-2022.
World bank (2022): GDP, available here:  https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GDP.MKTP.PP.KD, accessed 17-05-2022.</productionVolumeComment>
